title: FFIEC, 2007 Home Mortgage Loans in Washington DC CMSA by census tract, MSA, 2007
name: FFIEC, 2007 Home Mortgage Loans in Washington DC CMSA by census tract, MSA, 2007
description:
The polyshape file shows the number of home mortages by average amount of loans, average income and related demographics by census tract in the Washington DC MSA region for year 2007. 
By law all lenders have to report to Federal Financial Instition Examination Council (FFIEC) every home mortgage transaction carried out by them. The national level Home Mortgage Disclosure Act (HMDA) data available at the website runs into hundreds of gigabytes. The 2007 data for Wash DC MSA consists of combined mortgage transactions for Wash DC, Northern Virginia counties and suburban Maryland counties. The total number of loan records for 2007 are over 618 thousand.

author.source: The Federal Financial Institution Examination Council (FFIEC) website of Home Mortagage Disclosure Act (HMDA) data
